QUES 14. Still in your home directory, copy the entire directory play to a directory called work, preserving the symbolic link.

ranjit@ranjit-Vostro-1540:/home/work$ pwd
/home/work

ranjit@ranjit-Vostro-1540:/home$ mkdir work play
ranjit@ranjit-Vostro-1540:/home$cd play

ranjit@ranjit-Vostro-1540:/home/work$ln -s demo.txt demo_ln


ranjit@ranjit-Vostro-1540:/home/work$cd ..


ranjit@ranjit-Vostro-1540:/home$cp -r  play work 


ranjit@ranjit-Vostro-1540:/home$cd work 
ranjit@ranjit-Vostro-1540:/home/work$ls

demo.txt  demo_ln




